text: Bohumil Povejšil (born 15 July 1912, date of death unknown) was a Czech gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1936 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1912 births Category:Year of death missing Category:Czech male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Czechoslovakia Category:Gymnasts at the 1936 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Prague
